  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_188_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえはもう料理すんな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, that's enough cooking for you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38896</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_188_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんでさ。あたしだって、
みんなの役に立ちたいのに</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's your problem!? Everyone's starving,
you know! I want to be of use to them.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39408</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_188_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>役に立ちたいってんなら、お願いだから、
おとなしく座っててくれ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Not cooking will be of use to them! So please,
can you just sit still and be quiet.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40856</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_188_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Arche&gt;は他のところで、
みんなの役に立ってくれてるからいいんだって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Arche&gt;, he's saying that you'd be more useful helping
out somewhere else.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41548</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_188_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そ、そうですよ……
ここは私たちに任せて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Y-Yes, he's right...Leave the cooking to us.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41988</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_188_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうだ、この本、面白いぞ、
暇つぶしにちょうどいいから貸してやろう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why don't you help me out by keeping me company
while I read this book? It's really good for passing the time.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42780</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_188_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私もご一緒します</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Allow me to accompany you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43152</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_188_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何よぉ、ブー</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the hell...Hmph!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44892</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_188_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>５人がかりで&lt;Arche&gt;さんを
食事当番から引きずりおろした……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It took five people to pull &lt;Arche&gt; off of meal
duty...That's insane!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45192</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_188_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……すごい団結力だね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What amazing solidarity...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45428</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_005_188_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……こんな団結力とかって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You call this solidarity...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
